oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: W. J. Singleton pictured with 5 lb bass caught on Kentucky Lake, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of W. J. Singleton and a 5 lb. bass he caught near Dr. Burton's Perryville dock on Kentucky Lake. Singleton is in a fishing boat pictured with fishing equipment and is wearing a hat, eyeglasses, jacket and pants. There is the shoreline and water bank in the background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
